<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><!DOCTYPE paragraph PUBLIC "-//IFRS//DTD DITA Paragraph//EN" "../../../DocTypes/com.ifrs.doctype/dtd/paragraph.dtd"><paragraph id="IFRS01_D7"><paranum class="- topic/title paragraph/paranum "/><titlealts><navtitle>D7</navtitle></titlealts><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 1"/><data name="paranum" value="D7"/></prolog><body><variant base="F46426256" id="IFRS01_D7_V2" principles="no"> <p id="IFRS01_P0544">The elections in <xref base="F46426257" href="IFRS01_D5.dita#IFRS01_D5" id="IFRS01_X0692">paragraphs D5 and D6</xref> are also available for: </p> <ol outputclass="static" base="F46426258" id="IFRS01_L0050" type="lower-alpha"><li><li_value>(a)</li_value> <p base="F46426260" id="IFRS01_P0545">investment property, if an entity elects to use the cost model in <xref base="F46426261" href="../ias40/IAS40_TOC0001.dita#IAS40_TOC0001" id="IFRS01_X0693"><ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_number">IAS 40</ph> <ph outputclass="standard_title">Investment Property</ph></ph></xref>; </p> </li><li><li_value>(aa)</li_value> <p base="F46426358" id="IFRS01_P0547">right-of-use assets (<xref base="F46975760" href="../ifrs16/IFRS16_TOC.dita#IFRS16_TOC0001" id="IFRS01_X0698">IFRS 16 <ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_title">Leases</ph></ph></xref>);  and</p></li><li><li_value>(b)</li_value> <p base="F46426272" id="IFRS01_P0548">intangible assets that meet:</p> <ol outputclass="static" base="F46426273" id="IFRS01_L0051" type="lower-roman"><li><li_value>(i)</li_value> <p base="F46426275" id="IFRS01_P0549">the recognition criteria in <xref base="F46426276" href="../ias38/IAS38_TOC0001.dita#IAS38_TOC0001" id="IFRS01_X0700">IAS 38</xref> (including reliable measurement of original cost); and</p> </li><li><li_value>(ii)</li_value> <p base="F46426280" id="IFRS01_P0551">the criteria in <xref base="F46426281" href="../ias38/IAS38_TOC0001.dita#IAS38_TOC0001" id="IFRS01_X0702">IAS 38</xref> for revaluation (including the existence of an active market).</p> </li></ol> </li></ol> <p base="F46426284" id="IFRS01_P0555">An entity shall not use these elections for other assets or for liabilities.</p>  </variant></body></paragraph>